rows.label: bf11740100_0020
rows.name: I believe so. But it's got me thinking.

rows.label: bf11740100_0030
rows.name:
What is his aim in doing this?
Can it just be carnage for its own sake...?

rows.label: bf11740100_0040
rows.name:
Hikari...
Maybe you understand this better, as an Grail.

rows.label: bf11740100_0050
rows.name:
No. I might have the same power.
But that's all we have in common.

rows.label: bf11740100_0060
rows.name:
Could it be a reflection of something
in the depths of Marveni's mind, perhaps?

rows.label: bf11740100_0110
rows.name:
Let's go.
We can't afford to give him any more time...
